## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Virtual environment
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Environment files
.env
.env.*

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# Python tooling
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# Build artifacts
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

# Logs
*.log

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Docker
docker-compose.override.yml

# Kubernetes / Helm temp files
*.tgz

# ArgoCD / local exports
*.tmp
*.bak

# Terraform (if added later by mistake)
.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log

# Secrets / certs
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
secrets.yaml
values-secret.yaml

# macOS/Linux temp
*~